===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
{{wikipedia|Slug (disambiguation)|slug}}

# Any of many [[terrestrial]] [[pulmonate]] [[gastropod]] [[mollusk]]s, having no (or only [[rudimentary]]) [[shell]]
# A rarely used customary unit of [[mass]].
# A discrete quantity of one fluid that flows though the line surrounded by another.
# A [[bullet]].
# A counterfeit [[coin]], especially one used to steal from vending machines.
# A [[shot]] of a [[drink]], usually [[alcoholic]].
# A [[title]], [[name]] or [[header]]
# {{slang}} A [[lazy]] person, a [[sluggard]].
# (''Television editing'') A black screen
# (''Typesetting'') A piece of typemetal imprinted by a Linotype machine; also a black mark placed in the margin to indicate an error

